AEME

Aerial Evaluation & Measurement Engine

# scripts overview

## Directory layout
scripts/
├─ adsb/
│  ├─ aggregators/
│  ├─ analysis/
│  ├─ data_fetch/
│  └─ heatmap/
├─ config/
├─ plao/
├─ secrets/
├─ signals/
├─ tools/
├─ master.py
├─ phase_config.py
└─ structure

---

## Scripts (purpose / outputs)

### ADS-B aggregation
- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_aggregator.py`
  Purpose: daily AUC aggregation from past_log JSONL (max per day)
  Output: `output/adsb_daily_summary_raw.csv` (CSV)

- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_eval_pk_aggregator.py`
  Purpose: merge dist_1m + pos + movements into daily summary
  Output: `output/adsb_daily_summary.csv` (CSV)

- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_csv_patcher.py`
  Purpose: patch/extend columns in `adsb_daily_summary.csv`
  Output: overwrites input CSV

- `scripts/adsb/aggregators/adsb_local_traffic_proxy_gen.py`
  Purpose: generate local_traffic_proxy and merge into summary
  Output: `output/adsb_daily_summary_v2.csv` (CSV)

---

### ADS-B statistical evaluation (statsmodels)
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/stats/adsb_stats_eval.py`
  Purpose: effect evaluation using local_traffic_proxy
  Output: console only

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/stats/adsb_dynamic_eval.py`
  Purpose: effect estimation for an arbitrary intervention date
  Output: console only

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/stats/adsb_baseline_nb_eval.py`
  Purpose: baseline negative binomial model
  Output: `output/performance/baseline_nb_summary.txt`, `output/performance/baseline_nb_results.json`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/stats/adsb_distance_nb_eval.py`
  Purpose: distance-bin comparison (MWU + bootstrap)
  Output: `output/performance/distance_performance_summary.csv`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/stats/adsb_distance_binomial_eval.py`
  Purpose: distance-bin binomial model
  Output: `output/performance/distance_binomial_summary.csv`

---

### ADS-B Bayesian evaluation (PyMC/NumPyro)
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/bayesian/adsb_bayesian_eval.py`
  Purpose: Bayesian phase estimation
  Output: `output/performance/bayesian_phase_results.csv`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/bayesian/adsb_bayesian_dynamic_eval.py`
  Purpose: Bayesian estimation for an arbitrary intervention date
  Output: console only

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/bayesian/adsb_bayesian_advi_eval.py`
  Purpose: ADVI-based Bayesian estimation
  Output: console only

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/bayesian/adsb_bayesian_cuda_eval.py`
  Purpose: CUDA wrapper for phase comparison
  Output: `output/performance/bayesian_phase_results_cuda.csv`

---

### ADS-B change point detection (NumPyro/JAX)
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/change_points/adsb_detect_change_point.py`
  Purpose: single change point estimation
  Output: console/plots

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/change_points/adsb_detect_discovery_gpu.py`
  Purpose: change point detection with GPU/CPU switching
  Output: console/plots

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/change_points/adsb_detect_multi_change_points.py`
  Purpose: multi change point estimation (K=3)
  Output: console/plots

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/change_points/adsb_multi_discovery.py`
  Purpose: CPU-only multi change point estimation
  Output: console/plots

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/change_points/adsb_performance_discovery.py`
  Purpose: GPU/WSL multi change point estimation
  Output: console/plots

---

### ADS-B GPU evaluation (NumPyro/JAX)
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/gpu/adsb_bayesian_phase_cuda_eval.py`
  Purpose: GPU Bayesian phase estimation
  Output: `output/performance/bayesian_phase_results_cuda.csv`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/gpu/adsb_cuda_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: GPU change point visualization
  Output: `output/performance/adsb_cuda_evaluator_change_point.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/gpu/adsb_cuda_processor.py`
  Purpose: alternate GPU change point visualization
  Output: `output/performance/adsb_cuda_processor_change_point.png`

---

### ADS-B pipeline
- `scripts/master.py`
  Purpose: orchestration of the ADS-B evaluation pipeline
  Output: `output/performance/pipeline_runs.jsonl`

---

### ADS-B phase evaluation
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/phase/adsb_phase_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: phase-level improvement evaluation
  Output: `output/performance/phase_evaluator_results.csv`,
          `output/performance/phase_evaluator_report.txt`,
          `output/performance/phase_evaluator_boxplot.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/phase/adsb_manual_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: manual phase evaluation
  Output: console/plots

---

### ADS-B data fetch
- `scripts/adsb/data_fetch/get_opensky_traffic.py`
  Purpose: fetch OpenSky traffic data
  Output: `data/flight_data/airport_movements.csv`

---

### ADS-B heatmaps
- `scripts/adsb/heatmap/adsb_heatmap_generator.py`
  Purpose: single-day heatmap
  Output: `output/adsb_coverage_heatmap.html`

- `scripts/adsb/heatmap/adsb_daily_heatmap.py`
  Purpose: batch daily heatmaps
  Output: `output/heatmaps/*_heatmap.html`

- `scripts/adsb/heatmap/adsb_daily_heatmap_alt.py`
  Purpose: altitude-band heatmaps
  Output: `output/heatmaps/*_alt_heatmap.html`

---

### Consolidated report / coverage
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/reports/adsb_total_performance_reporter.py`
  Purpose: time-series report for AUC and signal
  Output: `output/tsuchiura_master_log_report.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/reports/adsb_polar_coverage_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: azimuth P95 distance trends
  Output: `output/coverage/coverage_trend.csv`, `output/coverage/coverage_trend_report.png`, `output/coverage/*_polar_p95.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/reports/adsb_vertical_profile_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: LOS efficiency trends
  Output: `output/vertical_profile/los_efficiency_trend.csv`, `output/vertical_profile/los_efficiency_trend_report.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/reports/adsb_fringe_decoding_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: long-range decoding statistics
  Output: `output/fringe_decoding/fringe_decoding_stats.csv`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/reports/adsb_fringe_decoding_quality_stats.py`
  Purpose: long-range decoding quality stats
  Output: console only

---

### Time-resolved
- `scripts/adsb/analysis/time_resolved/adsb_time_resolved_aggregator.py`
  Purpose: time-bin AUC/traffic aggregation
  Output: `output/time_resolved/adsb_timebin_summary.csv`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/time_resolved/adsb_time_resolved_mixed_eval.py`
  Purpose: mixed model analysis by time bin
  Output: `output/performance/time_resolved_performance.png`

- `scripts/adsb/analysis/time_resolved/adsb_time_resolved_detailed_report.py`
  Purpose: detailed time-bin report
  Output: `output/performance/time_bin_detailed_stats.csv`, `output/performance/time_resolved_detailed_plot.png`

---

### Signals
- `scripts/signals/collectors/signal_stats_aggregator.py`
  Purpose: signal strength aggregation
  Output: `output/adsb_signal_range_summary.csv`

- `scripts/signals/analysis/signal_range_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: distance-bin signal strength comparison
  Output: console only

- `scripts/signals/analysis/signal_quality_evaluator.py`
  Purpose: signal quality analysis
  Output: console only

---

### PLAO
- `scripts/plao/analysis/plao_distance_auc_eval.py`
  Purpose: PLAO pos distance-bin AUC aggregation/stats/plots
  Output: `output/plao/distance_auc/plao_daily_distance_auc_summary.csv`,
          `output/plao/distance_auc/plao_daily_distance_auc_long.csv`,
          `output/plao/distance_auc/plao_skipped_days.csv`,
          `output/plao/distance_auc/plao_distance_auc_stats_report.txt`

---

### Tools
- `scripts/tools/merge_output_for_ai/merge_output_for_ai.py`
  Purpose: merge text outputs under `output/` into a single Markdown
  Output: `<out_dir>/manifest.csv`, `<out_dir>/merged_for_ai.md`, `<out_dir>/merged_for_ai.zip`

---

## Notes
- Shared library code lives under `src/arena/lib` (import as `arena.lib`).
- `scripts/phase_config.py` is a compatibility shim for `arena.lib.phase_config`.
- Settings are in `scripts/config/phases.txt` and `scripts/config/settings.toml`.
